high_descs: Walk one step forward then walk to the fridge and turn to face it.
Open the fridge and pick up the tomato that's in there.
Turn right and then walk to the sink in the kitchen and stand facing it.
Cook the tomato in the microwave then take it back out and close the door.
Walk back over to the fridge.
Open the fridge and put the tomato back and close the fridge door.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked tomato in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn and go to the refrigerator on the left.
Open the refrigerator and pick up the tomato that is inside.
Turn around and go to the microwave that is above the sink.
Put the tomato in the microwave and microwave the tomato for three seconds.
Take the tomato and return to the refrigerator on the other side of the room.
Open the refrigerator and place the tomato on the the left side of the middle shelf.
anns.task_desc: Place a warmed tomato in the refrigerator.

high_descs: grab a tomato out from the fridge
bring the tomato over to the kitchen sink
place the tomato in the microwave above the sink, microwave it, and take it back out
bring the microwaved tomato over to the fridge
put the tomato in the lower portion of the fridge
anns.task_desc: place a microwaved tomato in the fridge
